                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: PF-012/PF-017 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "PF-001 Official performance source | Governance | Reject competing official record | Critical | Head of Performance. PF-002 Source reconciliation | Preventive | Block certification | Critical | Performance Operations. PF-003 Benchmark approval | Preventive | Block uncertified benchmark use | Critical | CIO/CCO. PF-004 Gross/net labeling | Preventive | Reject ambiguous presentation | High | Performance. PF-005 External/internal cash-flow classification | Preventive | Reclassify/hold calculation | Critical | Accounting. PF-006 Contribution reconciliation | Detective | Open attribution break | High | Performance. PF-007 Stale price | Preventive | DataRestricted | Critical | Valuation. PF-008 Late fee or financing adjustment | Detective | Restatement review | High | Accounting. PF-009 Retroactive benchmark change | Preventive | Enhanced approval/disclosure | Critical | CIO/CCO. PF-010 Selective period presentation | Preventive | Require approved period policy | Critical | CCO. PF-011 Restatement versioning | Evidence | Preserve prior version | Critical | Performance. PF-012 AI certification boundary | Preventive | Deny certification | Critical | Model Risk. PF-013 Unapproved attribution model | Governance | Reject production use | Critical | Model Risk. PF-014 FX source consistency | Preventive | Hold calculation | High | Performance. PF-015 Corporate action reconciliation | Detective | Open break | High | Operations. PF-016 Annualization minimum history | Preventive | Reject annualized display | High | Performance. PF-017 Cross-tenant performance access | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. PF-018 Manager self-certification | Preventive | Reject | Critical | CIO. PF-019 Missing methodology version | Evidence | Block certification | High | Performance. PF-020 Material error notification | Corrective | Notify downstream users | Critical | Head of Performance."
                            }
                        ]
